<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_367_r2l16">Wır dıe <expan>Burge<ex>r</ex></expan> etc . Bekennen etc Vmb ſölıch ladung vnd klag </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_367_r2l17">als <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> <expan>H<ex>er</ex>man</expan> von Prantenſtein <expan>Rıtt<ex>er</ex></expan> getan hat vnd tut vor </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_367_r2l18">dem lantgerıcht ʒu Awrbach auf weygenſeſʒ mıt <expan>ſeın<ex>er</ex></expan> ʒugehö = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_367_r2l19">rung vnd auf alles das wır vnd dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> daſelbs vnd ın dem </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_367_r2l20">ſelben <expan>lantger<ex>icht</ex></expan> ʒu Awrbach lıgent haben / daʒ wır <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_367_r2l21">lıeben <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> vnd <expan>Ratgeſelle<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>Pet<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>volkm<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> ynnern Rats vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_367_r2l22"><expan>Hannſ<ex>en</ex></expan> Hamerſtıl <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>gröſſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> rats geben <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd <expan>gebe<ex>n</ex></expan> vollen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_367_r2l23">vnd <expan>gancʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> gwalt vnd macht / <expan>dıeſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> vnſre vnd <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> <expan>güt<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_367_r2l24">vnd hab . von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd an <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> ſtat gen Jm <expan>ʒuu<ex>er</ex>antw<ex>ur</ex>ten</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_367_r2l25">vnd <expan>ʒuu<ex>er</ex>tretten</expan> ʒu <expan>gewin<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd ʒuuerluſt vnd ʒu allem rechten </ab>
